getAttributes

public BusinessObjectAttributes getAttributes(Context context)
                                       throws MatrixException
Get a list of all non-hidden attributes and the description for this BusinessObject. This interface populates the _hasChoices and _choices data members for attributes with range values, which can be expensive for attributes that have lengthy lists of range values or program range values. If _hasChoices and _choices are not needed, use the more efficient getAttributeValues methods.
Returns:
the list of Attributes and the description for this BusinessObject
